text: Quincy is an unincorporated community in Lewis County, Kentucky, United States. The community is located on Kentucky Route 8 and the Ohio River east of Vanceburg. Quincy has a post office with ZIP code 41166. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Lewis County, Kentucky Category:Unincorporated communities in Kentucky Category:Kentucky populated places on the Ohio River
title: Quincy, Kentucky
